## 7. Build Integration

### 7.1 Dependency Resolution (pnpm workspace)

The Cockpit and Control UI share the same pnpm workspace. Add the Control UI as a workspace dependency:

```json
// cockpitcockpit/package.json
{
  "dependencies": {
    "@openclaw/ui": "workspace:*"
  }
}
```

```json
// cockpitcockpit/tsconfig.json
{
  "compilerOptions": {
    "paths": {
      "@openclaw/ui/*": ["../ui/src/*"]
    }
  }
}
```

This allows direct imports from the Control UI source without duplication.

### 7.2 Code Splitting

Control UI admin routes are lazy-loaded to preserve Cockpit's fast initial load:

```typescript
// routes/admin/config.tsx
import { lazy } from "react";

// Lazy load the consumed Control UI config editor
const ConfigEditor = lazy(() => import("@openclaw/ui/routes/config"));

export default function ConfigPage() {
  return (
    <ThemeWrapper>
      <ConfigEditor />
    </ThemeWrapper>
  );
}
```

